Grazie @50bestdiscovery 
Si legge: 
Pino Cuttaia greets all his guests – only 40 in any sitting – personally, before delving into his memories to reinterpret classic Sicilian dishes with admirable creativity. The signature ‘Cloud of Caprese’ is a clever nod to classic tomato and mozzarella salad, while ‘Octopus on the Rocks’ sees whole tentacles presented on chickpea puree. A stone and wood fit out and views over the kitchen garden give Madia (meaning cupboard) a wholesome, natural feel, perfectly reflecting the restaurant’s philosophy.
